    "data": "اَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَيْكُمْ يَا اَهْلَ بَيْتِ النُّبُوَّةِ\nASSALAAMO A’LAYKUM YAA AHLA BAYTIN NOBUWWATE\nPeace be upon you, O Household of Prophethood,\nوَ مَوْضِعَ الرِّسَالَةِ \nWA MAWZEA’R RESAALATE \nlocation of the Divine mission,\nوَ مُخْتَلَفَ الْمَلَآئِكَةِ\nWA MUKHTALAFAL MALAAA-EKATE\nfrequently visited by the angels,\nوَ مَهْبِطَ الْوَحْىِ \nWA MAHBETIL WAHYE \ndestination of the Divine revelation,\nوَ مَعْدِنَ الرَّحْمَةِ\nWA MAA’-DENAR RAHMATE\ncore of mercy,\nوَ خُزَّانَ الْعِلْمِ \nWA KHUZZAANAL I’LME \nhoarders of knowledge,\nوَ مُنْتَهَى الْحِلمِ\nWA MUNTAHAL HILME\nultimate degree of forbearance,\nوَ اُصُوْلَ الْكَرَمِ \nWA OSOOLAL KARAME \norigins of generosity,\nوَ قَادَةَ الْاُمَمِ\nWA QAADATAL UMAME\nleaders of all nations,\nوَ اَوْلِيَآءَ النِّعَمِ \nWA AWLEYAAA-AN NE-A’ME \nsustainers of bounties,\nوَ عَنَاصِرَ الْاَبْرَارِ\nWA A’NAASERAL ABRAARE\nfoundations of the dutiful,\nوَ دَعَآئِمَ الْاَخْيَارِ \nWA DA-A’AA-EMAL AKHYAARE \npillars of the upright,\nوَسَاسَةَ الْعِبَادِ\nWA SAASATAL E’BAADE\nmaintainers of the servants (of Allah),\nوَ اَرْكَانَ الْبِلاَدِ \nWA ARKAANAL BELAADE \nprops of the lands,\nوَ اَبْوَابَ الْاِيْمَانِ \nWA ABWAABAL EEMAANE\ndoors to true faith,\nوَ اُمَنَآءَ الرَّحْمٰنِ \nWA OMANAAA-AR RAHMAANE \ntrustees of the All-beneficent (Allah),\nوَ سُلاَلَةَ النَّبِيِّيْنَ \nWA SOLAALATAN NABIYYEENA\ndescendants of the Prophets,\nوَ صِفْوَةَ الْمُرْسَلِيْنَ \nWA SIFWATAL MURSALEENA\nchoice of the Messengers,\nوَ عِتْرَةَ خِيَرَةِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ\nWA I’TRATA KHEYARATE RABBIL A’ALAMEENA\nand offspring of the select of the Lord of the worlds.\nوَ رَحْمْةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ \nWA RAHMATULLAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU\nAllah’s mercy and blessings, too, be upon you (all).\nاَلسَّلاَمُ عَلٰى اَئِمَّةِ الْهُدٰى\nASSALAAMO A’LAA A-IMMATIL HODAA\nPeace be upon the directors of right guidance,\nوَ مَصَابِيْحِ الدُّجٰى \nWA MASAABEEHID DOJAA \nthe lanterns in darkness,\nوَ اَعْلاَمِ التُّقٰى \nWA AA’-LAAMIT TOQAA\nthe patterns of piety,\nوَ ذَوِى النُّهٰى \nWA ZAWIN NOHAA \nthe owners of understanding,\nوَ اُولِى الْحِجٰى \nWA OLIL HEJAA\nthe endued with thought,\nوَ كَهْفِ الْوَرٰى \nWA KAHFIL WARAA WA \nthe havens for the peoples,\nوَ وَرَثَةِ اَلْاَنْبِيَآءِ\nWARASATIL AMBIYAAA-E\nthe inheritors of the Prophets,\nوَ الْمَثَلِ الْاَعْلٰى \nWAL MASALIL AA’-LAA \nthe perfect specimen,\nوَ الدَّعْوَةِ الْحُسْنٰى \nWADDAA’-WATIL HUSNAA\nthe most excellent call,\nوَ حُجَجِ اللهِ عَلٰى اَهْلِ الدُّنْيَا \nWA HOJAJILLAAHE A’LAA AHLID DUNYAA \nand the arguments of Allah against the inhabitants of the world,\nوَ الْاٰخِرَةِ وَ الْاُوْلٰى \nWAL AAKHERATE WAL OOLAA\nthe Hereafter, and the former world.\nوَ رَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ\nWA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU\nAllah’s mercy and blessings, too, be upon you (all).\nاَلسَّلاَمُ عَلٰى مَحَالِّ مَعْرِفَةِ اللهِ \nASSALAAMO A’LAA MAHAALLE MAA’-REFATILLAAHE\nPeace be upon the exponents of the recognition of Allah,\nوَ مَسَاكِنِ بَرَكَةِ اللهِ \nWA MASAAKENE BARAKATIL LAAHE \nthe centers of Allah’s blessing,\nوَ مَعَادِنِ حِكْمَةِ اللهِ \nWA MA-A’ADENE HIKMATIL LAAHE\nthe essence of Allah’s wisdom,\nوَ حَفَظَةِ سِرِّ اللهِ \nWA HAFAZATE SIRRIL LAAHE \nthe keepers of Allah’s secrets,\nوَ حَمَلَةِ كِتَابِ اللهِ\nWA HAMALATE KETAABIL LAAHE\nthe bearers of Allah’s Book,\nوَ اَوْصِيَآءِ نَبِىِّ اللهِ \nWA AWSEYAAA-E NABIYYILLAAHE\nthe successors of Allah’s Prophet,\nوَ ذُرِّيَّةِ رَسُوْلِ اللهِ \nWA ZURRIYYATE RASOOLIL LAAHE \nand the progeny of Allah’s Messenger,\nصَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ اٰلِهٖ\nSALLALLAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI\nmay Allah send blessings upon him and his Household.\nوَ رَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ\nWA RAHMATULLAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU\nAllah’s mercy and blessings, too, be upon them.\nاَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَى الدُّعَاةِ اِلَى اللهِ \nASSALAAMO A’LAD DO-A’ATE ELALLAAHE \nPeace be upon the callers to Allah,\nوَ الْاَدِلَّآءِ عَلٰى مَرْضَاتِ اللهِ \nWAL ADILLAAA-E A’LAA MARZAATIL LAAHE \nthe leaders to Allah’s pleasure,\nوَ الْمُسْتَقِرِّيْنَ فِىْ اَمْرِ اللهِ\nWAL MUSTAQIRREENA FEE AMRIL LAAHE\nthe abiders by Allah’s decree,\nوَ التَّآمِّيْنَ فِىْ مَحَبَّةِ اللهِ \nWATTAAAMMEENA FEE MAHABBATIL LAAHE\nthe perfect in love for Allah,\nوَ الْمُخْلِصِيْنَ فِىْ تَوْحِيْدِ اللهِ \nWAL MUKHLESEENA FEE TAWHEEDILLAAHE\nthe sincere in professing Allah’s Oneness,\nوَ الْمُظْهِرِيْنَ لِاَمْرِا للهِ وَ نَهْيِهٖ\nWAL MUZHEREEENA LE-AMRILLAAHE WA NAHYEHI\nthe manifesters of Allah’s orders and prohibitions,\nوَ عِبَادِهِ الْمُكْرَمِيْنَ \nWA E’BAADEHIL MUKRAMEENAL \nand Allah’s honored bondmen\nالَّذِيْنَ لاَ يَسْبِقُوْنَهُ بِالْقَوْلِ\nLAZEENA LAA YASBEQOONAHU BIL QAWLE\nwho speak not until He has spoken\nوَ هُمْ بِاَمْرِهٖ يَعْمَلُوْنَ \nWA HUM BE-AMREHI YAA’-MALOON \nand act by His command.\nوَ رَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ\nWA RAHMATULLAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU\nAllah’s mercy and blessings, too, be upon them.\nاَلسَّلاَمُ عَلَى الْاَئِمَّةِ الدُّعَاةِ \nASSALAAMO A’LAL A-IMMATID DO-A’ATE \nPeace be upon the Imams, the heralds,\nوَ الْقَادَةِ الْهُدَاةِ\nWAL QAADATIL HODAATE\nthe leaders, the guides,\nوَ السَّادَةِ الْوُلاَةِ \nWAS SAADATIL WOLAATE \nthe chiefs, the authorities,\nوَ الذَّادَةِ الْحُمَاةِ \nWAZ ZAADATIL HOMAATE\nthe defenders, the protectors,\nوَ اَهْلِ الذِّكْرِ \nWA AHLIZ ZIKRE \nthe people of the Reminder (i.e. the Qur’an),\nوَ اُوْلِى الْاَمْرِ \nWA OOLIL AMR \nthe men in authority,\nوَ بَقِيَّةِ اللهِ وَ خِيَرَتِهٖ \nWA BAQIYYATILLAAHE WA KHEYARATEHI\nthe left ones by Allah, His select,\nوَ حِزْبِهٖ وَ عَيْبَةِ عِلْمِهٖ \nWA HIZBEHI WA A’YBATE I’LMEHI \nHis party, the case of His knowledge\nوَ حُجَّتِهٖ وَ صِرَاطِهٖ \nWA HUJJATEHI WA SIRAATEHI \nHis argument, His path,\nوُ نُوْرِهٖ وَ بُرْهَانِهٖ \nWA NOOREHI WA BURHAANEHI \nHis light, and His proof.\nوَ رَحْمَةُ اللهِ وَ بَرَكَاتُهٗ\nWA RAHMATULLAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU\nAllah’s mercy and blessings, too, be upon them.\nاَشْهَدُ اَنْ لاَّ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ اللهُ \nASH-HADO AN LAA ELAAHA ILLALLAAHO \nI bear witness that there is no god save Allah;\nوَحْدَهُ لاَ شَرِيْكَ لَهٗ\nWAHDAHU LAA SHAREEKA LAHU\nOne and Only and having no partner with Him\nكَمَا شَهِدَ اللهُ لِنَفْسِهٖ\nKAMAA SHAHEDALLAAHO LENAFSEHI\njust as Allah has testified to His Oneness\nوَ شَهِدَتْ لَهُ مَلَآئِكَتُهٗ \nWA SHAHEDAT LAHU MALAAA-EKATOHU \nto which His angels\nوَ اُولُوا الْعِلْمِ مِنْ خَلْقِهٖ \nWA OLOOL I’LME MIN KHALQEHI\nand his knowledgeable creatures testify.\nلاَ اِلٰهَ اِلاَّ هُوَ الْعَزِيْزُ الْحَكِيْمُ\nLAA ELAAHA ILLAA HOWAL A’ZEEZUL HAKEEMO\nThere is no god save Him; the Almighty, the All-wise.\nوَ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُهُ الْمُنْتَجَبُ\nWA ASH-HADO ANNA MOHAMMADAN A’BDOHUL MUNTAJABO\nI also bear witness that Muhammad is His elect servant\nوَ رَسُوْلُهُ الْمُرْتَضٰى \nWA RASOOLOHUL MURTAZAA \nand His approved Messenger.\nاَرْسَلَهُ بِالْهُدٰى وَ دِيْنِ الْحَقِّ\nARSALAHU BIL HODAA WA DEENIL HAQQE\nHe sent him with right guidance and with the Religion of truth\nلِيُظْهِرَهُ عَلَى الدِّيْنِ كُلِّهٖ\nLE-YUZHERAHU A’LAD DEENE KULLEHI\nthat He may cause it to prevail over all religions\nوَ لَوْ كَرِهَ الْمُشْرِكُوْنَ \nWA LAW KAREHAL MUSHREKOONA\nhowever much the idol-worshippers may be averse.\nوَ اَشْهَدُ اَنَّكُمُ الْاَئِمَّةُ الرَّاشِدُوْنَ \nWA ASH-HADO ANNAKOMUL A-IMMATUR RAASHEDOONAL \nI also bear witness that you all are the Imams, rightly guiding,\nالْمَهْدِيُّوْنَ الْمَعْصُوْمُوْنَ\nMADHIYYOONAL MAA’-SOOMOONAL\nwell-guided, infallible,\nالْمُكَرَّمُوْنَ الْمُقَرَّبُوْنَ \nMOKARRAMOONAL MOQARRABOONAL\nhighly revered, drawn near (to Allah), \nالْمُتَّقُوْنَ الصَّادِقُوْنَ \nMUTTAQOONAS SAADEQOONAL \npious, veracious,\nالْمُصْطَفُوْنَ الْمُطِيْعُوْنَ لِلّٰهِ\nMUSTAFOONAL MOTEE-O’ONA LILLAAHIL \nwell-chosen, obedient to Allah,\nالْقَوَّامُوْنَ بِاَمْرِهِ\nQAWWAAMOONA BE-AMREHIL\nestablishing His rule,\nالْعَامِلُوْنَ بِاِرَادَتِهِ \nA’AMELOONA BE-ERAADATEHIL \nputting into practice His will,\nالْفَائِزُوْنَ بِكَرَامَتِهٖ \nFAA-EZOONA BE KARAAMATE HI\nand winning His honoring.\nاِصْطَفَاكُمْ بِعِلْمِهٖ \nISTAFAAKUM BE-I’LMEHI \nHe chose you on account of His (eternal) knowledge,\nوَ ارْتَضَاكُمْ لِغَيْبِهٖ\nWAR-TAZAAKUM LE-GHAYBEHI\napproved of you to maintain His unseen knowledge,\nوَاخْتَارَكُمْ لِسِرِهٖ \nWAKH-TAARAKUM LESIRREHI \nselected you to keep His secret,\nوَاجْتَبَاكُمْ بِقُدْرَتِهٖ\nWAJ-TABAAKUM BE QUDRATEHI\ndecided on you by means of His omnipotence,\nوَاَعَزَّكُمْ بِهُدَاهُ \nWA A-A’ZZAKUM BE HODAAHO \nequipped you with His guidance,\nوَخَصَّكُمْ بِبُرْهَانِهٖ\nWA KHASSAKUM   BEBURHAANEHI\ndistinguished you with His clear proofs,\nوَانْتَجَبَكُمْ لِنُوْرِهٖ \nWANTAJABAKUM LENOOREHI \nchose you to hold His Light,\nوَاَيَّدُكُمْ بِرُوْحِهٖ\nWA AYYADAKUM BIROOHIHI\nsupported you with His Holy spirit,\nوَرَضِيَكُمْ خُلَفَآءَ فِىْ اَرْضِهٖ \nWA RAZEYAKUM KHULAFAAA-A FEE ARZEHI \nand accepted you as vicegerents in His lands,\nوَ حُجَجًا عَلٰى بَرِيَّتِهٖ \nWA HUJAJAN A’LAA BARIYYATEHI\narguments against His beings,\nوَاَنْصَارًا لِّدِيْنِهٖ \nWA ANSAARAN LE DEENEHI \nsupporters of His religion,\nوَ حَفَظَةً لِّسِرِّهٖ\nWA HAFAZATAN LE SIRREHI\nkeepers of His secret,\nوَخَزَنَةً لِّعِلْمِهٖ\nWA KHAZANATAN LE I’LMEHI \nhoarders of His knowledge,\nوَ مُسْتَوْدَعًا لِّحِكْمَتِهٖ\nWA MUSTAWDA-A’N LE HIKMATEHI\nstores of His wisdom,\nوَ تَرَاجِمَةً لِّوَحْيِهٖ \nWA TARAAJEMATAN LE WAHYEHI \ninterpreters of His revelation,\nوَاَرْكَانًا لِّتَوْحِيْدِهٖ\nWA ARKAANAN LE TAWHEEDEHI\npillars of the profession of His Oneness,\nوَ شُهْدَآءَ عَلٰى خَلْقِهٖ \nWA SHOHADAAA-A A’LAA KHALQEHI \nwitnesses on His creatures,\nوَ اَعْلاَمًا لِّعِبَادِهٖ\nWA AA’-LAAMAN LE E’BAADEHI\nsigns for His servants,\nوَ مَنَارًا فِىْ بِلاَدِهٖ \nWA MANAARAN FEE BELAADEHI \ntorches in His lands,\nوَ اَدِلَّآءَ عَلٰى صِرَاطِهٖ\nWA ADILLAAA-A A’LAA SERAATEHI\nand directors to His path.\nعَصَمَكُمُ اللهُ مِنَ الزَّلَلِ \nA’SAMAKOMULLAAHO MENAZ ZALALE \nAllah has preserved you against slips,\nوَ اٰمَنَكُمْ مِنَ الْفِتَنِ\nWA AAMANAKUM MENAL FETANE\nsecured you against seditious matters,\nوَ طَهَّرَكُمْ مِنَ الْدَّنَسِ \nWA TAHHARAKUM MENAD DANASE \npurified you from dirt,\nوَ اَذْهَبَ عَنْكُمُ الرِّجْسَ\nWA AZHABA A’NKOMUR RIJSA\nremoved away from you uncleanness,\nوَ طَهَّرَكُمْ تَطْهِيْرًا \nWA TAHHARAKUM TATHEERAN  \nand purified you with a thorough purifying.\nفَعَظَّمْتُمْ جَلاَلَهِ \nFA A’ZZAMTUM JALAALAHU \nSo, you have glorified His majesty,\nوَ اَكْبَرْتُمْ شَانَهُ\nWA AKBARTUM SHAANAHU\ndeclared great His magnificence,\nوَ مَجَّدْتُمْ كَرَمَهُ \nWA MAJJADTUM KARAMAHU \nglorified His nobility,\nوَ اَدَمْتُمْ ذِكْرَهُ \nWA ADAMTUM ZIKRAHU \nperpetuated mentioning Him,\nوَ وَكَّدْتُمْ مِيْثَاقَهُ\nWA WAKKADTUM MEESAAQAHU\nconsolidated His covenant,\nوَاَحْكَمْتُمْ عَقْدَ طَاعَتِهٖ\nWA AHKAMTUM A’QDA TAA-A’TEHI \nmade firm your pledge of obedience to Him,\nوَ نَصَحْتُمْ لَهٗ فِى السِّرِّ وَالْعَلاَنِيَةِ \nWA NASAHTUM LAHU FIS SIRRE WAL A’LAANEYAH\nacted sincerely to Him privately and publicly,\nوَ دَعَوْتُمْ اِلٰى سَبِيْلِهٖ\nWA DA-A’WTUM ELAA SABEELEHI \ncalled unto His way\nبِالْحِكْمَةِ وَالْمَوْعِظَةِ الْحَسَنَةِ \nBIL HIKMATE WAL MAW-I’ZATIL HASANATE\nwith wisdom and fair admonition,\nوَ بَذَلْتُمْ اَنْفُسَكُمْ فِىْ مَرْضَاتِهٖ\nWA BAZALTUM ANFOSAKUM FEE MARZAATEHI\nsacrificed yourselves for the sake of attaining His pleasure,\nوَ صَبَرْتُمْ عَلٰى مَا اَصَابَكُمْ فِىْ جَنْبِهٖ\nWA SABARTUM A’LAA MAA ASAABAKUM FEE JANBEHI\nacted patiently towards what has befallen you for His sake,\nوَاَقَمْتُمُ الصَّلٰوةَ \nWA AQAMTOMUS SALAATA \nperformed the prayers,\nوَ اٰتَيْتُمُ الزَّكٰوةَ \nWA AATAYTOMUZ ZAKAATA\ndefrayed the poor-rate,\nوَ اَمَرْتُمْ بِالْمَعْرُوْفِ \nWA AMARTUM BIL MAA’-ROOFE \nenjoined the right,\nوَ نَهَيْتُمْ عَنِ الْمُنْكَرِ \nWA NAHAYTUM A’NIL MUNKARE\nforbade the wrong,\nوَ جَاهَدْتُمْ فِى اللهِ حَقَّ جِهَادِهٖ\nWA JAAHADTUM FILLAAHE HAQQA JEHAADEHI\nand strived in the way of Allah as exactly as striving should be\nحَتّٰى اَعْلَنْتُمْ دَعْوَتَهُ \nHATTAA AA’-LANTUM DA’-WATAHU \nuntil you made known His call,\nوَ بَيَّنْتُمْ فَرَآئِضَهٗ\nWA BAYYANTUM FARAAA-EZAHU\nrendered clear His obligations,\nوَ اَقَمْتُمْ حُدُوْدَهُ \nWA AQAMTUM HODOODAHU \nexecuted His provisions,\nوَ نَشَرْتُمْ شَرَايِعَ اَحْكَامِهٖ\nWA NASHARTUM SHARAAYE-A’ AHKAAMEHI\npropagated for the enacted laws of Him,\nوَ سَنَنْتُمْ سُنَّتَهُ \nWA SANANTUM SUNNATUHA \nacted out His rules,\nوَ صِرْتُمْ فِىْ ذٰلِكَ مِنْهُ اِلَى الرِّضَا \nWA SIRTUM FEE ZAALEKA MINHO ELAR REZAA\nattained His pleasure through carrying out all these matters,\nوَ سَلَّمْتُمْ لَهُ الْقَضَآءَ\nWA SALLAMTUM LAHUL QAZAAA-A\nsurrendered to His will,\nو صَدَّقْتُمْ مِنْ رُسُلِهٖ مَنْ مَضٰى \nWA SADDAQTUM MIN ROSOLEHI MAN MAZAA\nand confirmed the truth of the past Messengers of Him.\nفَالرَّاغِبُ عَنْكُمْ مَارِقٌ \nFAR-RAAGHEBO A’NKUM  MAAREQUN \nTherefore, whoever forsakes you is apostate,\nوَاللَّازِمُ لَكُمْ لاَحِقٌ \nWAL LAAZEMO LAKUM LAAHEQUN\nwhoever adheres to you will attain the destination,\nوَالْمُقَصِّرُ فِىْ حَقِّكُمْ زَاهِقٌ \nWAL MOQASSERO FEE HAQQEKUM ZAAHEQUN\nand whoever fails to carry out the duties towards you will perish.\nوَالْحَقُّ مَعَكُمْ وَ فِيْكُمْ \nWAL HAQQO MA-A’KUM WA FEEKUM \nVerily, the truth is always with you, amid you,\nوَ مِنْكُمْ وَ اِلَيْكُمْ\nWA MINKUM WA ELAYKUM\nfrom you, and to you.\nوَ اَنْتُمْ اَهْلُهٗ وَ مَعْدِنُهٗ \nWA ANTUM AHLOHU WA MA’-DENOHU \nYou are the people and the core of it (i.e. the truth).\nوَ مِيْرَاثُ النُّبُوَّةِ عِنْدَكُمْ\nWA MEERAASUN NOBUWWATE I’NDAKUM\nThe inheritance of Prophethood is with you.\nوَ اِيَابُ الْخَلْقِ اِلَيْكُمْ \nWA EYAABUL KHALQE ELAYKUM \nThe ultimate destination of the creatures is to you.\nوَ حِسَابُهُمْ عَلَيْكُمْ\nWA HISAABOHUM A’LAYKUM\nCalling them to account is your mission.\nوَ فَصْلُ الْخِطَابِ عِنْدَكُمْ \nWA FASLUL KHETAABE I’NDAKUM \nDecisive speech is with you.\nوَ اٰيَاتُ اللهِ لَدَيْكُمْ \nWA AAYAATULLAAHE LADAYKUM\nThe verses of Allah is in your possession.\nوَ عَزَآئِمُهٗ فِيْكُمْ \nWA A’ZAAA-EMOHU FEEKUM \nHis unavoidable decrees rely upon you.\nوَ نُوْرُهٗ وَ بُرْهَانُهٗ عِنْدَكُمْ \nWA NOOROHU WA BURHAANOHU I’NDAKUM\nHis light and proof are with you.\nوَاَمْرُهٗ اِلَيْكُمْ \nWA AMROHU ELAYKUM MAN \nHis authority is to you.\nمَنْ وَالَاكُمْ فَقَدْ وَالَى اللهَ\nWAALAAKUM FAQAD WA LALLAAHA\nWhoever declares loyalty to you has in fact declared loyalty to Allah,\nوَمَنْ عَادَاكُمْ فَقَدْ عَادَ اللهَ \nWA MAN A’ADAAKUM FAQAD A’ADALLAAHA\nwhoever shows enmity towards you has in fact shown enmity towards Allah,\nوَ مَنْ اَحَبَّكُمْ فَقَدْ اَحَبَّ اللهَ \nWA MAN AHABBAKUM FAQAD AHABBALLAAHA\nwhoever loves you has in fact loved Allah,\nوَ مَنْ اَبْغَضَكُمْ فَقَدْ اَبْغَضَ اللهَ \nWA MAN ABGAZAKUM FAQAD ABGAZALLAAHA\nwhoever hates you has in fact hated Allah,\nوَ مَنِ اعْتَصَمَ بِكُمْ فَقَدِ اعْتَصَمَ بِاللهِ \nWA MANEA’ TASAMA BEKUM FAQADEA’-TASAMA BILLAAHE\nand whoever holds fast to you has in fact held fast to Allah.\nاَنْتُمُ السَّبِيْلُ الْاَعْظَمُ \nANTOMUS SABEELUL AA’-ZAMO \nYou are the main means of approach the right way\nوَ الصِّرَاطُ الْاَقْوَمُ\nWAS SERAATUL AQWAMO\nand the most straight path,\nوَ شُهَدَآءُ دَارِالْفَنَآءِ \nWA SHOHADAAA-O DAARIL FANAAE \nthe witnesses of this abode of extinction,\nوَ شُفَعَآءُ دَارِالْبَقَآءِ\nWA SHOFA-A’AA-O DAARIL BAQAA-E\nthe intercessors in the abode of permanence,\nوَ الرَّحْمَةُ الْمَوْصُوْلَةُ \nWAR RAHMATUL MAWSOOLATO \nthe connected mercy,\nوَ الْاٰيَةُ الْمَخْزُوْنَةُ\nWAL AAYATUL MAKHZOONATO\nthe stored sign,\nوَالْاَمَانَةُ الْمَحْفُوْظَةُ \nWAL AMAANATUL MAHFOOZATO \nthe safeguarded deposit,\nوَ الْبَابُ الْمُبْتَلٰى بِهِ النَّاسُ\nWAL BAABUL MUBTALAA BEHIN NAASO\nand the door with which people are put to test.\nمَنْ اَتٰيكُمْ نَجٰى \nMAN ATAAKUM NAJAA \nWhoever comes to will have been saved\nوَ مَنْ لَمْ يَاْتِكُمْ هَلَكَ \nWA MAN LAM YAATEKUM HALAKA\nbut whoever refrains from joining you will have perished.\nاِلَى اللهِ تَدْعُوْنَ \nELALLAAHE   TAD-O’ONA \nTo Allah do you invite people,\nوَ عَلَيْهِ تَدُلُّوْنَ \nWA A’LAYHE TADULLOONA \ntowards him do you show the way,\nوَ بِهٖ تُؤْمِنُوْنَ\nWA BEHI TOO-MENOONA\nin Him do you believe,\nوَ لَهُ تُسَلِّمُوْنَ \nWA LAHU TOSALLEMOONA \nto Him do you submit,\nوَ بِاَمْرِهٖ تَعْمَلُوْنَ \nWA BE-AMREHI TA’-MALOONA\nupon His command do you act,\nوَ اِلٰى سَبِيْلِهٖ تُرْشِدُوْنَ \nWA ELAA SABEELEHI TURSHEDOONA \nto His path do you direct,\nوَ بِقَوْلِهٖ تَحْكُمُوْنَ \nWA BE QAWLEHI TAHKOMOONA\nand according to His saying do you judge.\nسَعَدَ مَنْ وَ الَاكُمْ \nSA-A’DA MAN WAALAAKUM \nHappy is he who is loyal to you,\nوَ هَلَكَ مَنْ عَادَاكُمْ \nWA HALAKA MAN A’ADAAKUM\ndesolate is he who forsakes you,\nوَ خَابَ مَنْ جَحَدَكُمْ \nWA KHAABA MAN JAHADAKUM \ndisappointed is he who denies you,\nوَ ضَلَّ مَنْ فَارَقَكُمْ\nWA ZALLA MAN FAARAQAKUM\nstraying off is he who separates himself from you,\nوَ فَازَ مَنْ تَمَسَّكَ بِكُمْ\nWA FAAZA MAN TAMASSAKA BEKUM\nwinner is he who adheres to you,\nوَ اَمِنَ مَنْ لَجَاَ اِلَيْكُمْ \nWA AMENA MAN LAJA-A  ELAYKUM\nsecured is he who resorts to you,\nوَ سَلِمَ مَنْ صَدَّقَكُمْ\nWA SALEMA MAN SADDAQAKUM\nsaved is he who gives credence to you,\nوَ هُدِىَ مَنِ اعْتَصَمَ بِكُمْ \nWA HODEYA MANEA’ TASAMA BEKUM\nand rightly guided is he who takes shelter in you.\nمَنِ اتَّبَعَكُمْ فَالْجَنَّةُ مَاْوَاهُ \nMANIT-TABA-A’KUM FAL JANNATO  MAAWAAHO\nAs to whoever follows you, Paradise will be his abode.\nوَ مَنْ خَالَفَكُمْ فَالنَّارُ مَثْوَاهُ \nWA MAN KHAALAFAKUM FAN-NAARO MASWAAHO\nAs to whoever dissents you, Hellfire will be his dwelling.\nوَ مَنْ جَحَدَكُمْ كَافِرٌ \nWA MAN JAHADAKUM KAAFERUN\nHe who denies you is unbeliever,\nوَ مَنْ حَارَبَكُمْ مُشْرِكٌ \nWA MAN HAARABAKUM MUSHREKUN\nhe who makes war against you is polytheist,\nوَ مَنْ رَدَّ عَلَيْكُمُ فِىْ اَسْفَلِ دَرَكٍ مِنَ الْجَحِيْمِ\nWA MAN RADDA A’LAYKUM FEE ASFALE DARAKIN MENAL JAHEEME\nand he who objects to you will be in the lowest tier of the burning fire.\nاَشْهَدُ اَنَّ هٰذَا سَابِقٌ لَكُمْ فِيْمَا مَضٰى\nASH-HADO ANNA HAAZAA SAABEQUN LAKUM FEEMAA MAZAA\nI bear witness that all the previous was pre-decided for you\nوَ جَارٍ لَكُمْ فِيْمَا بَقِىَ \nWA JAARIN LAKUM FEEMAA BAQEYA \nand it will continue in the future;\nوَ اَنَّ اَرْوَاحَكُمْ وَ نُوْرَكُمْ\nWA ANNA ARWAAHAKUM WA NOORAKUM\nand that your souls, your light,\nوَ طِيْنَتَكُمْ وَاحِدَةٌ \nWA TEENATAKUM WAAHEDATUN \nand your form are the same;\nطَابَتْ وَ طَهُرَتْ \nTAABAT WA TAHORAT\nblessed and purified,\nبَعْضُهَا مِنْ بَعْضٍ \nBA’-ZOHAA MIN BAA’-ZIN\nand one of the other.\nخَلَقَكُمُ اللهُ اَنْوَارًا \nKHALAQAKOMULLAAHO ANWAARAN \nAllah created you as lights;\nفَجَعَلَكُمْ بِعَرْشِهٖ مُحْدِقِيْنَ\nFAJA-A’LAKUM BE A’RSHEHI MOHDEQEENA\nHe then made you observe from His Throne\nحَتّٰى مَنَّ عَلَيْنَا بِكُمْ\nHATTA MANNA A’LAYNAA BEKUM\nuntil He endued us with the favor of your existence (among us)\nفَجَعَلَكُمْ فِىْ بُيُوْتٍ \nFAJ-A’LAKUM FEE BOYOOTIN \nand then placed you in houses\nاَذِنَ اللهُ اَن تُرْفَعَ \nAZENALLAAHO AN TURFA-A’ \nthat He allowed to be raised\nوَ يُذْكَرَ فِيْهَا اسْمُهٗ\nWA YUZKARA FEEHAS-MOHU\nand to have His Name mentioned therein.\nوَ جَعَلَ صَلَوَاتِنَا عَلَيْكُمْ \nWA JA-A’LA SALAWAATENAA A’LAYKUM\nHe also decided our invocation of blessings upon you \nوَ مَا خَصَّنَا بِهٖ مِنْ وِلاَيَتِكُمْ \nWA MAA KHASSANAA BEHI MIN WELAAYATEKUM\nand our loyalty to you\nطِيْبًا لِخَلْقِنَا \nTEEBAN LEKHALQENAA \nto be immaculacy of our creation,\nوَ طَهَارَةً لِاَنْفُسِنَا \nWA TAHAARATAN LE-ANFOSENAA\npurity of our souls,\nوَ تَزْكِيَةً لَنَا \nWA TAZKEYATAN LANAA \nrefinement of our manners,\nوَ كَفَّارَةً لِذُنُوْبِنَا \nWA KAFFAARATAN LE ZONOOBENAA\nand forgiveness of our sins.\nفَكُنَّا عِنْدَهُ مُسَلِّمِيْنَ بِفَضْلِكُمْ \nFAKUNNAA I’NDAHU MUSALLEMEENA BE FAZLEKUM\nWe have thus become, with Him, of those believing in your precedence\nوَ مَعْرُوْفِيْنَ بِتَصْدِيْقِنَا اِيَّاكُمْ \nWA MA’-ROOFEENA BE TASDEEQENAA IYYAAKUM\nand of those known for their giving credence to you.\nفَبَلَغَ اللهُ بِكُمْ اَشْرَفَ مَحَلِّ الْمُكَرَّمِيْنَ\nFABALAGHALLAAHO BEKUM ASHRAFA MAHALLIL MOKARRAMEENA\nThus, Allah has raised you to the most principled place of the honored ones,\nوَ اَعْلٰى مَنَازِلِ الْمُقَرَّبِيْنَ \nWA AA’-LAA MANAAZELIL MOQARRABEENA\nthe highest station of those drawn near to Him,\nوَ اَرْفَعَ دَرَجَاتِ الْمُرْسَلِيْنَ \nWA ARFA-A’ DARAJAATIL  MURSALEENA\nand the loftiest ranks of the Messengers\nحَيْثُ لاَ يَلْحَقُهٗ لاَحِقٌ \nHAYSO LAA YALHAQOHU  LAAHEQUN \nwhere none can ever reach you,\nوَ لاَ يَفُوْقُهٗ فَائِقٌ \nWA LAA YAFOOQOHU FAA-EQUN \nnor can anyone ever surpass you,\nوَ لاَ يَسْبِقُهٗ سَابِقٌ \nWA LAA YASBEQOHU SAABEQUN \nnor can anyone ever precede you,\nوَ لاَ يَطْمَعُ فِىْ اِدْرَاكِهٖ طَامِعٌ\nWA LAA YATMA-O’ FEE IDRAAKEHI TAAME-U’N\nno can anyone ever look forward to reaching your positions;\nحَتّٰى لاَ يَبْقٰى مَلَكٌ مُقَرَّبٌ \nHATTAA LAA YABQAA MALAKUN MOQARRABUN \ntherefore, no archangel,\nوَ لاَ نَبِىٌّ مُرْسَلٌ\nWA LAA NABIYYUN MURSALUN\ncommissioned Prophet,\nوَ لاَ صِدِّيْقٌ وَ لاَ شَهِيْدٌ \nWA LAA SIDDEEQUN WA LAA SHAHEEDUN \na veracious one, a martyr,\nوَ لاَ عَالِمٌ وَ لاَ جَاهِلٌ \nWA LAA A’ALEMUN WA LAA JAAHELUN \na knowledgeable one, an ignorant one,\nوَ لاَ دَنِىٌّ وَ لاَ فَاضِلٌ\nWA LAA DANIYYUN WA LAA FAAZELUN\nan inferior, a superior,\nوَ لاَ مُؤْمِنٌ صَالِحٌ \nWA LAA MOMENUN SAALEHUN \na righteous believer,\nوَ لاَ فَاجِرٌ طَالِحٌ\nWA LAA FAAJERUN TAALEHUN \na wicked sinner,\nوَ لاَ جَبَّارٌ عَنِيْدٌ \nWA LAA JABBAARUN A’NEEDUN \nan obstinate tyrant,\nوَ لاَ شَيْطَانٌ مَرِيْدٌ\nWA LAA SHAYTAANUN MAREEDUN\na devilish rebel,\nوَ لاَ خَلْقٌ فِيْمَا بَيْنَ ذٰلكَ شَهِيْدٌ\nWA LAA KHALQUN FEEMAA BAYNA ZAALEKA SHAHEEDUN\nor any other witnessing being among these classes – all of those\nاِلاَّ عَرَّفَهُمْ جَلاَلَةَ اَمْرِكُمْ \nILLAA A’RRAFAHUM JALAALATA AMREKUM \nwere informed by Allah about the majesty of your issue,\nوَ عَظِمَ خَطَرِكُمْ\nWA A’ZEMA KHATAREKUM \nthe importance of your standing,\nوَ كِبَرَ شَاْنِكُمْ \nWA KEBARA SHAANEKUM \nthe greatness of your prestige,\nوَتَمَامَ نُوْرِكُمْ\nWA TAMAAMA NOOREKUM\nthe thoroughness of your illumination,\nوَ صِدْقَ مَقَاعِدِكُمْ \nWA SIDQA MAQAA-E’DEKUM \nthe honesty of your position,\nوَ ثَبَاتَ مَقَامِكُمْ\nWA SABAATA MAQAAMEKUM \nthe firmness of your stance,\nوَ شَرَفَ مَحَلِّكُمْ وَ مَنْزِلَتِكُمْ عِنْدَهُ\nWA SHARAFA MAHALLEKUM WA MANZELATEKUM E’NDAHU \nthe honor of your station and position with Him,\nوَ كَرَامَتَكُمْ عَلَيْهِ \nWA KARAAMATAKUM A’LAYHE \nyour upstanding reputation with Him,\nوَ خَاصَّتَكُمْ لَدَيْهِ\nWA KHAASSATAKUM LADAYHE \nyour special position with Him,\nوَ قُرْبَ مَنْزِلَتِكُمْ مِنْهُ \nWA QURBA MANZELATEKUM MINHO \nand your close location to Him.\nبِاَبِىْ اَنْتُمْ وَ اُمِّىْ\nBE-ABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE\nMay my father, my mother,\nوَ اَهْلِىْ وَ مَالِىْ وَ اُسْرَتِىْ\nWA AHLEE WA MAALEE WA USRATEE\nmy kin, my property, and my family be ransoms for you.\nاُشْهِدُ اللهَ وَ اُشْهِدُكُمْ \nUSH-HEDULLAAHA WA USH-HEDOKUM \nI beseech Allah and I beseech you all to witness for me \nاَنِّىْ مُؤْمِنٌ بِكُمْ وَ بِمَا اٰمَنْتُمْ بِهٖ \nANNEE MOMENUN BEKUM WA BEMAA AAMANTUM BEHI \nthat I believe in you all and in that in which you believe,\nكَافِرٌ بِعَدُوِّكُمْ وَ بِمَا كَفَرْتُمْ بِهٖ \nKAAFERUN BE-A’DUWWEKUM WA BEMAA KAFARTUM BEHI \nI renounce your enemies and whatever you renounce,\nمُسْتَبْصِرٌ بِشَانِكُمْ\nMUSTABSERUN BE SHAANEKUM\nI am fully aware of your matter\nوَ بِضَلاَلَةِ مَنْ خَالَفَكُمْ \nWA BI-ZALAALATE MAN KHAALAFAKUM \nand of the deviation of those who oppose you,\nمُوَالٍ لَكُمْ وَ لِاَوْلِيَآئِكُمْ \nMOWAALIN LAKUM WA LE AWLEYAAA-EKUM \nI am loyalist to you and to your loyalists,\nمُبْغِضٌ لِاَعْدَآئِكُمْ وَ مُعَادٍ لَهُمْ \nMUBGEZUN LE AA’-DAAA-EKUM WA MO-A’ADIN LAHUM \nI hate your enemies and I show enmity towards them,\nسِلْمٌ لِمَنْ سَالَمَكُمْ\nSILMUN LEMAN SAALAMAKUM\nI am at peace with those who make peace with you,\nوَ حَرْبٌ لِمَنْ حَارَبَكُمْ \nWA HARBUN LEMAN HAARABAKUM \nI take the field against those who march against you,\nمُحَقِّقٌ لِمَا حَقَّقْتُمْ\nMOHAQQEQUN LEMAA HAQQAQTUM \nI accept as true that which you have decided as true,\nمُبْطِلٌ لِمَا اَبْطَلْتُمْ \nMUBTELUN LEMAA ABTALTUM \nI prove false that which you have decided as false,\nمُطِيْعٌ لَكُمْ \nMOTEE -U’N LAKUM \nI am obedient to you,\nعَارِفٌ بِحَقِّكُمْ\nA’AREFUN BE HAQQEKUM \nI recognize your right,\nمُقِرٌّ بِفَضْلِكُمْ \nMOQIRRUN BE FAZLEKUM \nI confess of your superiority,\nمُحْتَمِلٌ لِعِلْمِكُمْ \nMOHTAMELUN LE-I’LMEKUM \nI preserve your knowledge,\nمُحْتَجِبٌ بِذِمَّتِكُمْ \nMOHTAJEBUN BE ZIMMATEKUM \nI take refuge under your protective shelter,\nمُعْتَرِفٌ بِكُم \nMOA’-TAREFUN BEKUM \nI profess you,\nمُؤْمِنٌ بِاِيَابِكُمْ \nMOMENUN BE-EYAA BEKUM \nI believe in your coming back (to this world),\nمُصَدِّقٌ بِرَجْعَتِكُمْ \nMOSADDEQUN BERAJ-A’TEKUM\nI give credence to your return,\nمُنْتَظِرٌ لِاَمْرِكُمْ \nMUNTAZERUN LE  AMREKUM \nI am awaiting your issue,\nمُرْتَقِبٌ لِدَوْلَتِكُمْ \nMURTAQEBUN LE DAWLATEKUM \nI am expecting your rule,\nاٰخِذٌبِقَوْلِكُمْ \nAAKHEZUN BE QAWLEKUM \nI take in your sayings,\nعَامِلٌ بِاَمْرِكُمْ \nA’AMELUN BE AMREKUM \nI carry out your orders,\nمُسْتَجِيْرٌ بِكُمْ\nMUSTAJEERUN BEKUM \nI take shelter in you,\nزَائِرٌ لَكُمْ \nZAA ERUN LAKUM \nI make visits to you\nلاَئِذٌ عَائِذٌ بِقُبُوْرِكُمْ\nLAA-EZUN A’A-EZUN BE QOBOOREKUM \nI resort to and seek protection in your graves,\nمُسْتَشْفِعٌ اِلَى اللهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ بِكُمْ\nMUSTASHFE-U’N ELALLAAHE A’ZZA WA JALLA BEKUM\nI seek your intercession for me with Allah the Almighty and All-majestic,\nوَ مُتَقَرِّبٌ بِكُمْ اِلَيْهِ \nWA MOTAQARREBUN BEKUM ELAYHE \nI seek nearness to Him in your names,\nوَ مُقَدِّمُكُمْ اَمَامَ طَلِبَتِىْ \nWA MOQADDEMOKUM AMAAMA TALEBATEE \nI provide you as my means for seeking fulfillment of my desires,\nوَ حَوَآئِجِىْ وَ اِرَادَ تِىْ\nWA HAWAAA-EJEE WA ERAADATEE\nneeds, and wishes,\nفِىْ كُلِّ اَحْوَالِىْ وَ اُمُوْرِىْ \nFEE KULLE AHWAALEE WA OMOOREE \nin all of my manners and affairs,\nمُؤْمِنٌ بِسِرِّكُمْ وَ عَلاَنِيَتِكُمْ\nMOMENUN BE SIRREKUM WA A’LAANEYATEKUM \nI believe in your invisibility, visibility,\nوَ شَاهِدِكُمْ وَ غَآئِبِكُمْ \nWA SHAAHEDEKUM WA GAAA-EBEKUM \npresence, absence,\nوَ اَوَّلِكُمْ وَ اٰخِرِكُمْ \nWA AWWALEKUM WA AAKHEREKUM \nfirst, and last of you;\nوَ مُفَوِّضٌ فِىْ ذٰلِكَ كُلِّهٖ اِلَيْكُمْ \nWA MOFAWWEZUN FEE ZAALEKA KULLEHI ELAYKUM \nand I confide all that to you\nوَ مُسَلِّمٌ فِيْهِ مَعَكُمْ\nWA MUSALLEMUN FEEHI MA-A’KUM \nand submit to all of it with you.\nوَ قَلْبِىْ لَكُمْ مُسَلِّمٌ \nWA QALBEE LAKUM MUSALLEMUN \nMy heart is subservient to you,\nوَ رَاْيِىْ لَكُمْ تَبَعٌ\nWA RAAYEE LAKUM TABA-U’N \nmy opinion is following yours,\nوَ نُصْرَ تِىْ لَكُمْ مُعَدَّةٌ\nWA NUSRATEE LAKUM MO-A’DDATUN\nand my support to you is all set\nحَتّٰى يُحْيِىَ اللهُ تَعَالٰى دِيْنَهُ بِكُمْ\nHATTAA YUH-YEYALLAAHO TA-A’ALAA DEENAHU BEKUM\nuntil Allah the All-exalted restores His religion to life through you,\nوَ يَرُدَّكُمْ فِىْ اَيَّامِهٖ \nWA YARUDDAKUM FEE AYYAAMEHI \nbrings you back again in His days,\nوَ يُظْهِرَكُمْ لِعَدْلِهٖ\nWA YUZHERAKUM LE-A’DLEHI\nallows you to appear for (establishing) His justice,\nوَ يُمَكِّنَكُمْ فِىْ اَرْضِهٖ \nWA YUMAKKENAKUM FEE ARZEHI \nand gives you power to rule in His land.\nفَمَعَكُمْ مَعَكُمْ \nFAMA-A’KUM MA-A’KUM\nSo, I am (always) with you, with you,\nلاَ مَعَ غَيْرِكُمْ \nLAA MA-A’ GHAYREKUM \nbut not with anyone other than you.\nاٰمَنْتُ بِكُمْ \nAAMANTO BEKUM \nI have full faith in you,\nوَ تَوَلَّيْتُ اٰخِرَكُمْ بِمَا تَوَلَّيْتُ بِهٖ اَوَّلَكُمْ\nWA TAWALLAYTO AAKHERAKUM BEMAA TAWALLAYTO BEHI AWWALAKUM\nand I declare my loyalty to the last of you just as I declared it to the first of you.\nوَ بَرِئْتُ اِلٰى اللهِ عَزَّوَجَلَّ \nWA BAREA-TO ELALLAAHE A’ZZA WA JALLA \nIn the presence of Allah the Almighty and All-majestic, I repudiate\nمِنْ اَعْدَآئِكُمْ\nMIN AA’-DAAA-EKUM\nyour enemies,\nوَ مِنَ الْجِبْتِ وَ الطَّاغُوْتِ \nWA MENAL JIBTE WAT TAAGOOTE \nall idols, false deities,\nوَ الشَّيَاطِيْنِ\nWASH- SHAYAATEENE\nthe devils,\nوَ حِزْبِهِمُ الظَّالِمِيْنَ لَكُمْ \nWA HIZBEHIMUZ ZAALEMEENA LAKUM \nand their party who have wronged you,\nوَ الْجَاحِدِيْنَ لِحَقِّكُمْ\nWAL JAAHEDEENA LE HAQQEKUM\ndenied your rights,\nوَ الْمَارِقِيْنَ مِنْ وَلاَيَتِكُمْ \nWAL MAAREQEENA MIN WELAAYATEKUM \napostatized from your (divinely commissioned) leadership,\nوَ الْغَاصِبِيْنَ لِاِرْثِكُمْ \nWAL GAASEBEENA LE-IRSEKUM \nusurped your inheritance,\nوَ الشَّاكِّيْنَ فِيْكُمُ \nWASH SHAAKKEENA FEEKUM \narisen doubts about you,\nالْمُنْحَرِفِيْنَ عَنْكُمْ \nWAL MUNHAREFEENA A’NKUM \nand deviated from you,\nوَ مِنْ كُلِّ وَ لِيْجَةٍ دُوْنَكُمْ\nWA MIN KULLE WALEEJATIN DOONAKUM\nand (I repudiate) any adherence to anyone other than you,\nوَ كُلِّ مُطَاعٍ سِوَاكُمْ \nWA KULLE MOTAA-I’N SEWAAKUM \nany obeyed one save you,\nوَ مِنَ الْاَئِمَّةِ الَّذِيْنَ يَدْعُوْنَ اِلَى النَّارِ \nWA MENAL A-IMMATIL LAZEENA YAD-O’ONA ELAN NAARE \nand the leaders who call to Hellfire.\nفَثَبَّتَنِىَ اللهُ اَبَدًا مَا حَيِيْتُ \nFASABBATANEYALLAAHO ABADAN MAA HAYEEYTO \nMay Allah make me firm forever as long as I am alive\nعَلٰى مُوَالاَتِكُمْ\nA’LAA MOWAALAATEKUM\non loyalty to you,\nوَ مَحَبَّتِكُمْ وَ دِيْنِكُمْ \nWA MAHABBATEKUM WA DEENEKUM \nlove for you, and on your religion.\nوَ وَفَّقَنِىْ لِطَاعَتِكُمْ\nWA WAFFAQANEE LETAA-A’TEKUM \nMay He grant me success in obedience to you,\nوَ رَزَقَنِىْ شَفَاعَتَكُمْ \nWA RAZAQANEE SHAFAA-A’TAKUM \nendue me with your intercession,\nوَ جَعَلَنِىْ مِنْ خِيَارِ مَوَالِيْكُمُ \nWA JA-A’LANEE MIN KHEYAARE MAWAALEEKOMUT \nmake me of the best of your loyalists\nالتَّابِعِيْنَ لِمَا دَعَوْتُمْ اِلَيْهِ\nTAABE-E’ENA LEMAA DA-A’WTUM ELAYHE\nwho carry out all that to which you have called,\nوَ جَعَلَنِىْ مِمَّنْ يَقْتَصُّ اٰثَارَكُمْ \nWA JA-A’LANEE MIMMAN YAQTASSO AASAARAKUM \nand make me of those who are tracking your footsteps,\nوَ يَسْلُكُ سَبِيْلَكُمْ \nWA YASLOKO SABEELAKUM \ntaking your path,\nوَ يَهْتَدِىْ بِهُدٰيكُمْ \nWA YAHTADI BE HODAAKUM \nfollowing your guidance,\nوَ يَحْشُرُ فِىْ زُمْرَتِكُمْ\nWA YOHSHARO  FEE ZUMRATEKUM\n(and those who are) resurrected in your group,\nوَ يَكِرُّ فِىْ رَجْعَتِكُمْ \nWA YAKIRRO FEE RAJ-A’TEKUM \ngiven the chance to appear again in your Return,\nوَ يُمَلَّكُ فِىْ دَوْلَتِكُمْ\nWA YOMALLAKO FEE DAWLATEKUM\ngiven authority in your administration,\nوَ يُشَرَّفُ فِىْ عَافِيَتِكُمْ \nWA YOSHARRAFO FEE A’AFEYATEKUM \nhonored to live under your sound supervision,\nوَ يُمَكَّنُ فِىْ اَيَّامِكُمْ\nWA YOMAKKANO FEE AYYAAMEKUM\ngiven power in your days,\nوَ تَقِرُّ عَيْنُهٗ غَدًا بِرُؤْيَتِكُمْ \nWA TAQIRRO A’YNOHU GADAN BERO-YATEKUM \nand having their eyes delighted by seeing you in the morrow.\nبِاَبِىْ اَنْتُمْ وَ اُمِّىْ\nBE ABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE \nMay my father, mother,\nوَ نَفْسِىْ وَ اَهْلِىْ وَ مَالِىْ \nWA NAFSEE WA AHLEE WA MAALEE \nsoul, family, and possessions be ransoms for you.\nمَنْ اَرَادَ اللهَ بَدَءَ بِكُمْ \nMAN ARAADALLAAHA  BADA-A BEKUM \nWhoever desires for Allah should begin with you,\nوَ مَنْ وَحَّدَهُ قَبِلَ عَنْكُمْ\nWA MAN WAHHADAHU QABELA A’NKUM\nwhoever professes His Oneness should accept your instructions,\nوَ مَنْ قَصَدَهُ تَوَجَّهَ بِكُمْ \nWA MAN QASADAHU TAWWAJJAHA BEKUM \nand whoever heads for Him should make you the means to Him.\nمَوَالِىَّ لاَ اُحْصِىْ ثَنَآئَكُمْ \nMAWAALIYYA LAA OHSEE SANAAA-AKUM \nO my masters, I cannot count your merits\nوَ لاَ اَبْلُغُ مِنَ الْمَدْحِ كُنْهَكُمْ\nWA LAA ABLOGO MENAL MAD-HE KUNHAKUM\nand I cannot attain the utmost of praise of you\nوَ مِنَ الْوَصْفِ قَدْرَكُمْ \nWA MENAL WASFE QADRAKUM \nand the utmost of the description of your actual value,\nوَ اَنْتُمْ نُوْرُ الْاَخْيَارِ\nWA ANTUM NOORUL AKHYAARE\nsince you are the light of the upright ones,\nوَ هُدَاةُ الْاَبْرَارِ \nWA HODAATUL ABRAARE \nthe guides of the pious ones,\nوَ حُجَجُ الْجَبَّارِ \nWA HOJAJUL JABBAARE \nand the arguments of the Supreme Lord.\nبِكُمْ فَتَحَ اللهُ \nBEKUM FATAHALLAAHO \nWith you has Allah begun creation\nوَ بِكُمْ يَخْتِمُ اللهُ \nWA BEKUM YAKHTEMULLAAHU \nand with you will He seal it.\nوَ بِكُمْ يُنَزِّلُ الْغَيْثَ \nWA BEKUM YUNAZZELUL GAYSA \nFor your sake does He pour down rain,\nوَ بِكُمْ يُمْسِكُ السَّمَآءَ اَنْ تَقَعَ عَلَى الْاَرْضِ اِلاَّ بِاِذْنِهٖ\nWA BEKUM YUMSEKUS SAMAAA-A AN TAQA-A’ A’LAL ARZE ILLAA BE IZNEHI \nfor your sake does He withhold the heavens from falling on the earth except by His permission,\nوَ بِكُمْ يُنَفِّسُ الْهَمَّ \nWA BEKUM YONAFFESUL HAMMA \nand out of consideration for you does He dismiss agonies\nوَ يَكْشِفُ الضُّرَّ \nWA YAKSHEFUZ ZURRA\nand relieves harms.\nوَ عِنْدَكُمْ مَا نَزَلَتْ بِهٖ رُسُلُهٗ \nWA I’NDAKUM MAA NAZALAT BEHI ROSOLOHU \nIn your possession is all that which His Messengers brought down\nوَ هَبَطَتْ بِهٖ مَلَآئِكَتُهٗ \nWA HABATAT BEHI MALAAA-EKATOHU \nand with which His angels descended.\nوَ اِلٰى جَدِّكُمْ بُعِثَ الرُّوْحُ الْاَمِيْنُ \nWA ELAA JADDEKUM BO-E’SAR ROOHUL AMEENO \nTo your forefather was the Honest Spirit sent.\nاٰتَاكُمُ اللهُ مَا لَمْ يُؤْتَ اَحَدًا مِّنَ الْعَالَمِيْنَ \nAATAAKOMUL LAAHO MAA LAM YO’TI AHADAN MENAL A’ALAMEENA \nAllah has given you that which He has not given to any one all over the worlds.\nطَاْطَاَ كُلُّ شَرِيْفٍ لِشَرَفِكُمْ \nTAATA-A KULLO SHAREEFIN LE SHARAFEKUM \nAll highborn ones nod down their heads before your noble lineage,\nوَ بَخَعَ كُلُّ مُتَكَبِّرٍ لِطَاعَتِكُمْ\nWA BAKHA-A’ KULLO MUTAKABERRIN LETAA-A’TEKUM\nall arrogant ones submit to the obedience to you,\nوَ خَضَعَ كُلُّ جَبَّارٍ لِفَضْلِكُمْ \nWA KHAZA-A’ KULLO J’ABBAARIN LEFAZLEKUM \nall insolent oppressors succumb to your excellence,\nوَ ذَلَّ كُلُّ شَىْءٍ لَكُمْ\nWA ZALLA KULLO SHAY-IN LAKUM\nall things are humiliated before you,\nوَ اَشْرَقَتِ الْاَرْضُ بِنُوْرِكُمْ \nWA ASHRAQATIL ARZO BE NOOREKUM  \nthe earth has been lit up with your light,\nوَ فَازَ الْفَائِزُوْنَ بِوِلاَيَتِكُمْ \nWA FAAZAL FAA-EZOONA BE WELAAYATEKUM \nand the winners have attained triumph due to their loyalty to you.\nبِكُمْ يُسْلَكُ اِلَى الرِّضْوَانِ\nBEKUM YUSLAKO ELAR RIZWAANE\nThrough you can the way to Paradise be taken\nوَ عَلٰى مَنْ جَحَدَ وِلاَيَتِكُمْ غَضَبُ الرَّحْمٰنِ\nWA A’LAA MAN JAHADA WELAAYATEKUM GHAZABUR RAHMAANE\nand the ire of the All-beneficent is poured on whoever has denied your (divinely commissioned) leadership.\nبِاَبِىْ اَنْتُمْ وَ اُمِّىْ \nBE ABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE \nMay my father, mother,\nوَ وَنَفْسِىْ وَ اَهْلِىْ وَ مَالِىْ\nWA NAFSEE WA AHLEE WA MAALEE \nsoul, family, and possessions be ransoms for you.\nذِكْرُكُمْ فِى الذَّاكِرِيْنَ\nZIKRO KUM FIZ  ZAAKEREENA\nyour mention is within the mention of others.\nوَ اَسْمَآوٴُكُمْ فِى الْاَسْمَآءِ \nWA ASMAAA-OKUM FIL ASMAAA-E \nYour names are called along with other names.\nوَ اَجْسَادُكُمْ فِى الْاَجْسَادِ\nWA AJSAADOKUM FIL AJSAADE\nYour figures appear among other figures.\nوَ اَرْوَاحُكُمْ فِى الْاَرْوَاحِ \nWA ARWAAHOKUM FIL ARWAAHE\nYour souls are among other souls.\nوَ اَنْفُسُكُمْ فِى النُّفُوْسِ \nWA ANFOSOKUM FIN NOFOOSE \nYour selves are among other selves.\nوَ اٰثَارُكُمْ فِى الْاٰثَارِ \nWA AASAAROKUM FIL AASAAR AATHAARE \nYour traditions are among other traditions.\nوَ قُبُوْرُكُمْ فِى الْقُبُوْرِ \nWA QOBOOROKUM FIL QOBOORE \nYour graves are among other graves.\nفَمَا اَحْلٰى اَسْمَآئَكُمْ \nFAMAA AHLAA ASMAAA-AKUM \nBut how gracious your names are!\nوَ اَكْرَمَ اَنْفُسَكُمْ \nWA AKRAMA ANFOSAKUM \nHow noble your souls are!\nوَ اَعْظَمَ شَاْنَكُمْ \nWA AA’-ZAMA SHAANAKUM \nHow superior your affairs are!\nوَ اَجَلَّ خَطَرَكُمْ \nWA AJALLA KHATARAKUM \nHow majestic your stations are!\nوَ اَوْفٰى عَهْدَكُمْ \nWA AWFAA A’HDAKUM WA \nHow dependable your covenants are!\nوَ اَصْدَقَ وَعْدَكُمْ \nWA ASDAQA WA’-DAKUM \nHow truthful your promises are!\nكَلاَمُكُمْ نُوْرٌ \nKALAAMOKUM  NOORUN \nYour words are illumination.\nوَ اَمْرُكُمْ رُشْدٌ \nWA AMROKUM RUSHDUN  \nYour affairs are (leading to) orthodoxy.\nوَ وَصِيَّتُكُمُ التَّقْوٰى \nWA WASIYYATOKOMUT TAQWAA \nYour precepts are piety.\nوَ فِعْلُكُمُ الْخَيْرُ \nWA FEA’-LOKOMUL KHAYRO \nYour deeds are all good.\nوَ عَادَتُكُمُ الْاِحْسَانُ \nWA A’ADATOKOMUL EHSAAN \nYour habits are charity.\nوَ سَجِيَّتُكُمُ الْكَرَمُ \nWA SAJIYYATOKOMUL KARAMO \nYour nature is generosity.\nوَ شَاْنُكُمُ الْحَقُّ \nWA SHAANOKOMUL HAQQO \nYour issue is truth,\nوَ الصِّدْقُ وَ الرِّفْقُ \nWAS SIDQO WAR RIFQO  \nhonesty, and lenience.\nوَ قَوْلُكُمْ حُكْمٌ وَ حَتْمٌ \nWA QAWLOKUM HUKMUN WA HATMUN \nYour words are judgments and decisiveness.\nوَ رَاْيُكُمْ عِلْمٌ وَ حِلْمٌ وَ حَزْمٌ \nWA RAAYOKUM I’LMUN WA HILMUN WA HAZMUN \nYour views are (based upon) knowledge, temperance, and forethought.\nاِنْ ذُكِرَ الْخَيْرُ كُنْتُمْ اَوَّلَهٗ\nIN ZOKERAL KHAYRO KUNTUM AWWALAHU \nWhenever goodness is mentioned, you are its initiation,\nوَ اَصْلَهٗ وَ فَرْعَهٗ\nWA ASLAHU WA FAR-A’HU \norigin, branch,\nوَ مَعْدِنَهٗ وَ مَاْوَاهُ وَ مُنْتَهَاهُ \nWA MA’-DENAHU WA MAAWAAHO WA MUNTAHAAHO \nessence, center, and ultimate.\nبِاَبِىْ اَنْتُمْ وَ اُمِّىْ وَ نَفْسِىْ \nBI-ABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE WA NAFSEE \nMay my father, mother, and soul be ransoms for you.\nكَيْفَ اَصِفُ حُسْنَ ثَنَآئِكُمْ\nKAYFA ASEFU HUSNA SANAAA-EKUM\nHow shall I describe the excellence of your merits\nوَ اُحْصِىْ جَمِيْلَ بَلَآئِكُمْ \nWA UHSEE JAMEELA BALAAA-EKUM \nand define the beauty of your conferrals?\nوَ بِكُمْ اَخْرَجَنَا اللهُ مِنَ الذُّلِّ \nWA BEKUM AKHRAJANALLAAHO MENAZ ZULLE \nIt is on account of you that Allah has pulled us out of degradation,\nوَ فَرَّجَ عَنَّا غَمَرَاتِ الْكُرُوْبِ\nWA FARRIJ A’NNAA GAMARAATIL KOROOBE\nremoved from us the clutches of hardships,\nوَ اَنْقَذَنَا مِنْ شَفَا جُرُفِ الْهَلَكَاتِ \nWA ANQAZANAA MIN SHAFAA JOROFIL HALAKAATE \nand saved us from the brink of the pit of perditions\nوَ مِنَ النَّارِ\nWA MENAN NAARE\nand from the Fire.\nبِاَبِىْ اَنْتُمْ وَ اُمِّىْ وَ نَفْسِىْ \nBE ABEE ANTUM WA UMMEE WA NAFSEE \nMay my father, mother, and soul be ransoms for you.\nبِمُوَالاَتِكُمْ عَلَّمَنَا اللهُ مَعَالِمَ دِيْنِنَا \nBE MOWAALAATEKUM A’LLAMANALLAAHO MA-A’ALEMA DEENENAA \nThrough our loyalty to your leadership, Allah has taught us the features of our religion\nوَ اَصْلَحَ مَا كَانَ فَسَدَ مِنْ دُنْيَانَا\nWA ASLAHA MAA KAANA FASADA MIN DUNYAANAA\nand has set aright the spoiled items of our worldly lives.\nوَ بِمُوَالاَتِكُمَ تَمَّتِ الْكَلِمَةُ \nWA BE MOWAALAATEKUM TAMMATIL KALEMATO\nThrough our loyalty to your leadership, the Word has been perfected,\nوَ عَظُمَتِ النِّعْمَةُ \nWA A’ZOMATIN NEA’-MATO \nthe grace has become great,\nوَ ائْتَلَفَتِ الْفُرْقَةُ\nWAA-TALAFATIL FURQATO \nand the discord has turned into alliance.\nوَ بِمُوَالاَتِكُمْ تُقْبَلُ الطَّاعَةُ الْمُفْتَرَضَةُ\nWA BEMOWAALAATEKUM TUQBALUT TAA-A’TUL MUFTARAZATO\nThrough our loyalty to your leadership, the obligatory obedience (to Allah) is accepted.\nوَ لَكُمُ الْمَوَدَّةُ الْوَاجِبَةُ \nWA LAKOMUL MAWADDATUL WAAJEBATO \nTo you alone are the obligatory affection,\nوَ الدَّرَجَاتُ الرَّفِيْعَةُ\nWAD DARAJAATUR RAFEE-A’TO\nthe elevated ranks,\nوَ الْمَقَامُ الْمَحْمُوْدُ \nWAL MAQAAMUL MAHMOODO \nthe praiseworthy standing,\nوَ الْمَكَانُ الْمَعْلَوْمُ عِنْدَ اللهِ عَزَوَجَلَّ \nWAL MAKAANUL MA’-LOOMO I’NDALLAAHE A’ZZA WA JALLA \nthe renowned station with Allah the Almighty and All-majestic,\nوَ الْجَاهُ الْعَظِيْمُ\nWAL JAAHUL A’ZEEMO\nthe topmost prestige,\nوَ الشَّاْنُ الْكَبِيْرُ \nWASH SHAANUL KABEERO \nthe supreme station,\nوَ الشَّفَاعَةُ الْمَقْبُوْلَةُ\nWASH SHAFAA-A’TUL MAQBOOLATO\nand the admitted intercession.\nرَبَّنَا اٰمَنَّا بِمَا اَنْزَلْتَ \nRABBANAA AAMANNAA BEMAA ANZALTA \nO our Lord, we believe in that which You have sent down\nوَ اتَّبَعْنَا الرَّسُوْلَ\nWATTABAA’-NAR RASOOLA\nand we follow the Messenger;\nفَاكْتُبْنَا مَعَ الشَّاهِدِيْنَ \nFAK-TUBNAA MA-A’SH SHAAHEDEEN \nso, write our names among those who bear witness.\nرَبَّنَا لاَ تُزِغْ قُلُوْبَنَا بَعْدَ اِذْ هَدَيْتَنَا \nRABBANAA LAA TUZIGH QOLOOBANAA BA’-DA IZ HADAYTANAA \nOur Lord, cause not our hearts to stray after You have guided us,\nوَ هَبْ لَنَا مِنْ لَّدُنْكَ رَحْمَةً\nWA HAB LANAA MIN LADUNKA RAHMATAN \nand bestow upon us mercy from Your Presence.\nاِنَّكَ اَنْتَ الْوَهَّابُ \nINNAKA ANTAL WAHHAABO \nLo! You, only You, are the Bestower.\nسُبْحَانَ رَبِّنَا \nSUBHAANA RABBENAA \nGlory be to our Lord\nاِنْ كَانَ وَعْدُ رَبِّنَا لَمَفْعُوْلاً\nIN KAANA WA’-DO RABBENAA LAMAF-O’OLAN \nfor in fact the promise of our Lord immediately takes effect.\nيَا وَلِىَّ اللهِ \nYAA WALIYYALLAAHE \nO vicegerent of Allah!\nاِنَّ بَيْنِىْ وَ بَيْنَ اللهِ عَزَّوَجَلَّ ذُنُوْبًا \nINNA BAYNEE WA BAYNALLAAHE A’ZZA WA JALLA ZONOOBAN \nThere stand between me and Allah the Almighty and All-majestic, sins\nلاَ يَاْتِىْ عَلَيْهَا اِلاَّ رِضَاكُمْ\nLAA YAATEE A’LAYHAA ILLAA REZAAKUM\nthat cannot be demolished except by attaining your satisfaction.\nفَبِحَقِّ مَنِ ائْتَمَنَكُمْ عَلٰى سِرِّهٖ\nFABEHAQQE MANEA-TAMANAKUM A’LAA SIRREHI \nTherefore, [I beseech you] in the name of the One Who has entrusted you with His secret,\nوَ اسْتَرْعَاكُمْ اَمْرَخَلْقِهٖ \nWASTAR-A’AKUM AMRA KHALQEHI \nassigned you to supervise the affairs of His creatures,\nوَ قَرَنَ طَاعَتَكُمْ بِطَاعَتِهٖ\nWA QARANA TAA-A’TAKUM BE TAA-A’TEHI\nand attached the obedience to Him with the obedience to you,\nلَمَّا اسْتَوْهَبْتُمْ ذُنَوْبِىْ\nLAMMAS TAWHABTUM ZONOOBEE \nto (please) endue me with the favor of absolving my sins\nوَ كُنْتُمْ شُفَعَآئِىْ \nWA KUNTUM SHOFA-A’A-EE \nand to be my intercessors,\nفَاِنِّىْ لَكُمْ مُطِيْعٌ \nFA INNEE LAKUM MOTEE-U’N \nfor I am obedient to you.\nمَنْ اَطَاعَكُمْ فَقَدْ اَطَاعَ اللهَ\nMAN ATAA-A’KUM FAQAD ATAA-A’LLAAHA\nHe who obeys you has in fact obeyed Allah,\nوَ مَنْ عَصَاكُمْ فَقَدْ عَصَى اللهَ \nWA MAN A’SAAKUM FAQAD A’SALLAAHA \nhe who disobeys you has in fact disobeyed Allah,\nوَ مَنْ اَحَبَّكُمْ فَقَدْ اَحَبَّ اللهَ \nWA MAN AHABBAKUM FAQAD AHABBALLAAHA\nhe who loves you has in fact loved Allah,\nوَ مَنْ اَبْغَضَكُمْ فَقَدْ اَبْغَضَ اللهَ\nWA MAN ABGHAZAKUM FAQAD ABGHAZAL LAAHA\nand he who hates you has in fact hated Allah.\nاَللّٰهُمَّ اِنِّىْ لَوْ وَجَدْتُ شُفَعَآءَ \nALLAAHUMMA INNEE LAW WAJADTO SHOFA-A’A-A \nO Allah, had I known interceders\nاَقْرَبَ اِلَيْكَ مِنْ مُّحَمَّدٍ وَّ اَهْلِ بَيْتِهِ \nAQRABA ELAYKA MIN MOHAMMADIN WA AHLE BAYTEHIL \nthat are closer to You than Mu¦ammad and his Household\nالْاَخْيَارِ الْاَئِمَّةِ الْاَبْرَارِ\nAKHYAARIL A-IMMATIL ABRAARE \nthe virtuous and pious Imams,\nلَجَعَلْتُهُمْ شُفَعَآئِىْ \nLAJA-A’LTOHUM SHOFA-A’A-EE \nI would have chosen them as my intercessors.\nفَبِحَقِّهِمُ الَّذِىْ اَوْجَبْتَ لَهُمْ عَلَيْكَ\nFA BEHAQQEHIMUL LAZEE AWJABTA LAHUM A’LAYKA\nSo, [I beseech You] in the name of their Right that You have made obligatory upon You,\nاَسْئَلُكَ اَنْ تُدْخِلَنِىْ فِىْ جُمْلَةِ الْعَارِفِيْنَ بِهِمْ وَ بِحَقِّهِمْ \nAS-ALOKA AN TUDKHELANEE FEE JUMLATIL A’AREFEENA BEHIM WA BEHAQQEHIM \n(please) include me with the group of those who recognize their Right and them\nوَ فِىْ زُمْرَةِ الْمَرْحُوْمِيْنَ بِشَفَاعَتِهِمْ \nWA FEE ZUMRATIL MARHOOMEENA BE SHAFAA-A’TEHIM \nand with the assembly of those who are shown mercy owing to their (i.e. Muhammad and his Household) intercession.\nاِنَّكَ اَرْحَمُ الرَّحِمِيْنَ\nINNAKA ARHAMUR RAAHEMEENA\nVerily, You are the most merciful of all those who show mercy.\nوَ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّ اٰلِهِ الطَّاهِرِيْنَ\nWA SALLALLAAHO A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHIT TAAHEREENA \nMay Allah send blessings upon Mu¦ammad and his immaculate Household\nوَ سَلَّمَ تَسْلِيْمًا كَثِيْرًا \nWA SALLAMA TASLEEMAN KATHEERAN \nand send His thorough peace upon them.\nوَ حَسْبُنَا اللهُ وَ نِعْمَ الْوَكِيْلُ\nWA HASBONALLAAHO WA NEA’-MAL WAKEELO.\nAllah is Sufficient for us! Most Excellent is He in Whom we trust.", 
    "title": "Ziyarat e Jamiah Kabeerah"
}